# EAS Build ignore file
# Excludes files from the source upload to EAS, even if they're tracked in git.
# Note: Metro tree-shakes unreferenced files at runtime, so anything not
# imported wouldn't ship in the JS bundle anyway. This list is about reducing
# upload size and Metro scan surface, not runtime bundle composition.

# Legacy code we keep around for reference but never want shipping
_old/
_old/**
